list.name: Changes
list.comment:
feat: Add Ryby app models, migrations, views, and templates; wire up homepage and admin
- Introduce Ryby and Okres_ochronny models with initial migration and admin registration. - Add index view rendering ryby.html, listing fish and protective periods (with filter in template). - Create templates and static assets (style.css, image reference) and load them via STATIC. - Add CSV seed files for ryby and okres_ochronny. - Update urls to expose index at root and normalize settings/entry files to double-quote style.
